{"tid":2374704,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟稱經過4年時間 歐洲在白宮終於有朋友　形容是新曙光","createTime":"2021-01-21T12:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T01:39:49.000Z","uid":75656,"like":3,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"dee9fd48a40f0190eafc9573162480bb2e04de72","tid":2374704,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:13:36.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨的拜登稍後宣誓就任美國總統，歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩表示，經過4年時間，歐洲在白宮有一位朋友，形容是新曙光。<br />\n<br />\n馮德萊恩說，歐盟準備好與美國開展新關係，美國打算重新加入巴黎氣候協定是跨大西洋關係的非常重要起點，又希望美國與歐盟共同合作，抗擊新型肺炎疫情。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲理事會主席米歇爾說，跨大西洋關係過去4年遭受極大影響，世界變得更複雜、更不穩和不可預測，呼籲拜登新政府，與歐盟在應對氣候變化、疫情、數碼轉型、安全、自由與人權方面達成新公約，建立更強大的歐洲和美國，以及更美好的世界。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571424-20210120.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571424-20210120.htm&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=a4a663c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571424-20210120.htm&h=d56855d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571424-20210120.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6d7c355159e33bb4d85911514ae42a38359dbd5f","tid":2374704,"uid":80724,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:14:32.000Z","msg":"終於係白宮搵到朋友一齊奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b4d6158aede8967e5fe0ce8b5e83b72b264fc8","tid":2374704,"uid":54721,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:14:37.000Z","msg":"有得搵笨先算朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd51b4e8067f5c7cd57083dac5210c69ce4c3ac8","tid":2374704,"uid":70786,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:16:55.000Z","msg":"留意翻<br />\n馮德萊恩有份推中歐合作<br />\n50+民主派被捕時聲都唔聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56be702910b4747da853a6e9bdf6214d95f11eec","tid":2374704,"uid":387026,"like":3,"dislik